00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:25,560
During the Lantern Festival,
there is no curfew.

876
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:28,080
The city with lights
will be even more beautiful.

877
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,260
Then,

878
00:35:29,660 --> 00:35:30,900
I will take you to see it again.

879
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,420
Really?

880
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:36,100
Thank you. You're so kind.

881
00:36:00,900 --> 00:36:02,970
(Shaoguang's Food Notes)

882
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:04,230
(Why not eat pork?)

883
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,240
(The people of Yong'an are stubborn.)

884
00:36:06,240 --> 00:36:07,750
(Lamb is the best in the world.)

885
00:36:07,750 --> 00:36:10,010
(Pork can never be on the table.)

886
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:12,530
(Before,
