887
00:36:12,530 --> 00:36:14,290
(boiled, and roasted.)

888
00:36:14,290 --> 00:36:18,310
(Even the slightest mistake in breeding,
slaughtering, and deodorizing)

889
00:36:18,310 --> 00:36:19,570
(can ruin the taste.)

890
00:36:19,570 --> 00:36:21,830
(But I want the people of Yong'an)

891
00:36:21,830 --> 00:36:24,600
(to easily enjoy delicious meat,)

892
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:26,620
(so pork is something I can start with.)

